event = {
	id = 2802320
	random = no

	trigger = {
		OR = { #5% chances in 1942, 100% afterwards
			AND = {
				random = 5
				year = 1942
				NOT = { year = 1943 }
			}
			year = 1943
		}
		control = { province = 464 data = -1 }
	}

	name = "Resource"
	desc = "A resource change in province under our control"
	style = 0	
	
	date = { day = 1 month = january year = 1937 }
	offset = 15
	deathdate = { day = 29 month = december year = 1948 }

	action_a = {
		name = "Ok"
		command = { type = add_prov_resource which = 464 value = 5 where = oil } #Hollabrun
	}
}

event = {
	id = 2800000
	random = no

	trigger = {
		OR = {
			AND = {
				month = 0
				NOT = { month = 4 }
				random = 5
			}
			AND = {
				month = 4
				NOT = { month = 8 }
				random = 7
			}
			AND = {
				month = 8
				NOT = { month = 10 }
				random = 10
			}
			month = 11
		}
		control = { province = 1166 data = -1 } # Edinburgh
		year = 1937
	}

	name = "Resource"
	desc = "A resource change in province under our control"
	style = 0	
	
	date = { day = 1 month = january year = 1937 }
	offset = 15
	deathdate = { day = 29 month = december year = 1948 }

	action_a = {
		name = "Ok"
		command = { type = add_prov_resource which = 1166 value = 2 where = metal }
	}
}

	random = no

	trigger = {
		OR = {
			AND = {
				month = 0
				NOT = { month = 4 }
				random = 5
			}
			AND = {
				month = 4
				NOT = { month = 8 }
				random = 7
			}
			AND = {
				month = 8
				NOT = { month = 10 }
				random = 10
			}
			month = 11
		}
		control = { province = 6608 data = -1 } # Val d'Or
		year = 1939
	}

	name = "Resource"
	desc = "A resource change in province under our control"
	style = 0	
	
	date = { day = 1 month = january year = 1939 }
	offset = 15
	deathdate = { day = 29 month = december year = 1948 }

	action_a = {
		name = "Ok"
		command = { type = add_prov_resource which = 6608 value = 1 where = metal }
	}
}

	random = no

	trigger = {
		OR = {
			AND = {
				month = 0
				NOT = { month = 4 }
				random = 5
			}
			AND = {
				month = 4
				NOT = { month = 8 }
				random = 7
			}
			AND = {
				month = 8
				NOT = { month = 10 }
				random = 10
			}
			month = 11
		}
		control = { province = 62 data = -1 } # Orleans
		year = 1940
	}

	name = "Resource"
	desc = "A resource change in province under our control"
	style = 0	
	
	date = { day = 1 month = january year = 1940 }
	offset = 15
	deathdate = { day = 29 month = december year = 1948 }

	action_a = {
		name = "Ok"
		command = { type = add_prov_resource which = 62 value = 1 where = metal }
	}
}

			AND = {
				month = 0

		}

		OR = {
			AND = {
				month = 0
				NOT = { month = 4 }
				random = 5
			}
			AND = {
				month = 4
				NOT = { month = 8 }
				random = 7
			}
			AND = {
				month = 8
				NOT = { month = 10 }
				random = 10
			}
			month = 11
		}
		control = { province = 804 data = -1 } # Maracaibo
		year = 1941
	}

	name = "Resource"
	desc = "A resource change in province under our control"
	style = 0	
	
	date = { day = 1 month = january year = 1941 }
	offset = 15
	deathdate = { day = 29 month = december year = 1948 }

	action_a = {
		name = "Ok"
		command = { type = add_prov_resource which = 804 value = 2 where = energy }
		command = { type = add_prov_resource which = 804 value = 17 where = oil }
	}
}

	id = 2801820
	random = no

	trigger = {
		OR = {
			AND = {
				month = 0
				NOT = { month = 4 }
				random = 5

				month = 4
				NOT = { month = 8 }
